{"tid":415353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【執葉律師】譚香文去信選管會、ICAC、星加坡及英國律師會投訴何君堯","createTime":"2017-09-27T02:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T05:25:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"571e6b8f9468664cac2e9efdfd417b2d7438d9ad","tid":415353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"譚香文 Mandy Tam 分享了譚香文的帖子。<br />\n16小時 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n我剛也去信新加坡律師會（The Law Society of Singapore），建議其就何君堯涉嫌失實陳述，自稱為「新加坡執業律師」，採取跟進行動，包括進行調查和適當的紀律聆訊及處分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22007749_10214370015306664_8504668282652607699_n.jpg?oh=eecd6682c9d9cceb625e7f814a048657&amp;oe=5A480F90\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22007749_10214370015306664_8504668282652607699_n.jpg%3Foh%3Deecd6682c9d9cceb625e7f814a048657%26oe%3D5A480F90&h=3d86f30f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚香文 Mandy Tam 新增了 2 張相片。<br />\n23 小時 &middot; 香港 &middot; <br />\n已致函選舉管理委員會、廉政公署、香港律師會及英國律師監管機構SRA，舉報或投訴何君堯，有關其自稱「新加坡和英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師」，涉嫌發放虛假及誤導性陳述一事，嚴正要求上述有關當局盡速進行調查，以及相應跟進行動，例如檢控及紀律聆訊/處分。已收到選舉事務處之暫時回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21765066_1486959501396980_7165992483602723293_n.jpg?oh=c64f449e4e5f9de2dc8f0aca2051a5e2&amp;oe=5A3D4DCB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21765066_1486959501396980_7165992483602723293_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dc64f449e4e5f9de2dc8f0aca2051a5e2%26oe%3D5A3D4DCB&h=504e024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21766729_1486959531396977_8223217608834598718_n.jpg?oh=1e7ca4d095320f0261aeb04601379edb&amp;oe=5A3D4971\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21766729_1486959531396977_8223217608834598718_n.jpg%3Foh%3D1e7ca4d095320f0261aeb04601379edb%26oe%3D5A3D4971&h=e9b0571c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f51bb36a79e48c5348e6763dc634e0f3aeeace0","tid":415353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmandytamheungman&d=RzJSJSfdRjlWHHp1t%2FBGPiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=27126934\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mandytamheungman</a>"},{"pid":"78acbd8a0b744985558c2cd92bd7edc4ec83bfd7","tid":415353,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce436dd489fc2ebddbc97af60104ba90b5ae6a13","tid":415353,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a094315ad679d22fb16bd38916435dd7c6c8edb","tid":415353,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"雖然譚香文個形象都唔係好㗎啦<br />\n不過對付無牌執業律師就點都要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9935a147ecb47e38953e654b2fa83c2d268e71d","tid":415353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5579583e036f0b91e23b995c94ff03600a861719","tid":415353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然譚香文個形象都唔係好㗎啦<br />\n不過對付無牌執業律師就點都要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唯一一個代議士出手<br />\n譚香文係咪退出左公民黨？<br />\n<br />\n楊ON Q仲係人地做佢吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ae3824848b53678432e95991a36f5a8c530b9f","tid":415353,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"熱狗成件事 有無做過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/